# Commercial Performance Review – Due Diligence Case Study

A commercial due diligence analysis of a simulated international retail business.

SQL queries were used to extract and diagnose key performance drivers, followed by Excel-based financial modelling and dashboard development to assess revenue growth, margin dynamics, and acquisition viability.

The analysis identifies operational issues and proposes quantified value creation opportunities across pricing, cost structure, and segment performance.

