Key Insights

- Revenue growing at ~24% CAGR with stable margins (~11–12%)
- Office Supplies underperforming with high revenue but low profit contribution
- Tables identified as the only loss-making sub-category (-8% margin)
- Revenue concentration in specific regions introduces geographic risk
- Customer mix diversified with no segment exceeding 55% of revenue

